'''''snād''''' is a [[Nandorin]] word meaning "a wounding, a wound".<ref name=PE19>{{PE|19}}, p. 91</ref>

== Etymology ==
The word derives from [[Common Eldarin]] ''snagdē'', from [[Sundocarme|root]] SNAG- ("wound, gash").<ref name=PE19/>

